'''斯泰蘭蒂斯有限公司'''（Stellantis N.V.），是一家[[跨國公司|跨國]][[汽車產業|汽車]]製造商，總部位於荷蘭[[阿姆斯特丹|阿姆斯特丹]]，<ref name= Fox /><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/merged-fiat-chrysler-psa-company-to-be-named-stellantis-11594837979 |title=Fiat Chrysler to Be Renamed Stellantis After Merger With PSA |work=[[Wall_Street_Journal|Wall Street Journal]] |date=2020-07-15 |accessdate=2021-04-03 |archive-date=2021-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131040339/https://www.wsj.com/articles/merged-fiat-chrysler-psa-company-to-be-named-stellantis-11594837979 |dead-url=no }}</ref>於2021年由義大利-美國公司[[飛雅特克萊斯勒汽車|飛雅特克萊斯勒汽車]]與法國公司[[寶獅雪鐵龍集團|寶獅雪鐵龍集團]]合併而成的大型汽車集團，雙方各出資一半。<ref name= Fox>{{cite web |url=https://www.foxbusiness.com/lifestyle/fiat-chrysler-and-psa-group-rename-merged-automaker-stellantis |title=Fiat Chrysler and PSA Group rename merged automaker ‘Stellantis’ |website=[[Fox_Business|Fox Business]] |date=2020-07-16 |access-date=2021-04-03 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128015211/https://www.foxbusiness.com/lifestyle/fiat-chrysler-and-psa-group-rename-merged-automaker-stellantis |dead-url=no }}</ref>該集團擁有廣泛的汽車品牌組合：[[Abarth|阿巴斯]]、[[阿尔法·罗密欧|阿尔法·罗密欧]]、[[克萊斯勒|克萊斯勒]]、[[雪鐵龍|雪鐵龍]]、[[道奇|道奇]]、[[DS汽車|DS汽車]]、[[菲亞特|菲亞特]]、{{link-en|菲亞特專業|Fiat Professional}}、[[吉普汽車|吉普汽車]]、[[藍旗亞|藍旗亞]]、[[瑪莎拉蒂|瑪莎拉蒂]]、{{link-en|莫帕爾|Mopar}}、[[歐寶|歐寶]]、[[標緻|標緻]]、[[公羊貨車|公羊貨車]]及[[佛賀汽車|佛賀汽車]]。「斯泰蘭蒂斯」名稱專門用於標識公司實體，而集團下各品牌的名稱和標誌則維持不變。<ref name=Fox/>

該公司擁有40萬名員工，業務遍及130多個國家，在30個國家擁有製造工廠。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Overview |url=https://www.stellantis.com/en/group/overview |access-date=2021-01-19 |website=Stellantis |archive-date=2021-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429165140/https://www.stellantis.com/en/group/overview |dead-url=no }}</ref>該集團計劃在2021年底之前推出39款電動汽車。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Stellantis: Building a world leader in sustainable mobility |url=https://www.stellantis.com/en/news/press-releases/2021/january/stellantis-building-a-world-leader-in-sustainable-mobility |access-date=2021-01-19 |website=Stellantis |archive-date=2021-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211124203205/https://www.stellantis.com/en/news/press-releases/2021/january/stellantis-building-a-world-leader-in-sustainable-mobility |dead-url=no }}</ref>

